        <item>
            <title>賽車遊戲《Test Drive Unlimited》相隔 12 年推新作回歸，以香港島做主題、超逼真還原街景</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/05/31/tdusc-hk/game-channel/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=tdusc-hk</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/05/31/tdusc-hk/game-channel/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Ngan Ivan]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 31 May 2024 12:30:51 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[遊戲情報]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[賽車]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[遊戲]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1239519</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">由 KT Gaming 製作的賽車遊戲 Test Drive Unlimited 系列繼 12 年前的 Test Drive: Ferrari Racing Legends 後，終於推出新作 Test Drive Unlimited Solar Crown（TDUSC）。本次新作將賽車舞台搬到香港島，是系列首次將背景放在亞洲。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1239530" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/ss_ee5f1c1466411cd25-694x390.jpg" alt="Test Drive Unlimited Solar Crown" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/ss_ee5f1c1466411cd25-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/ss_ee5f1c1466411cd25.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1239531 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/ss_f434b3987297b6bd0-1-694x390.jpg" alt="Test Drive Unlimited Solar Crown" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/ss_f434b3987297b6bd0-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/ss_f434b3987297b6bd0-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1239532 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/ss_37420489a7069c1f2-694x390.jpg" alt="Test Drive Unlimited Solar Crown" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/ss_37420489a7069c1f2-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/ss_37420489a7069c1f2.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/1249970/Test_Drive_Unlimited_Solar_Crown/">Steam</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">遊戲發行商 Nacon 公佈的預告片中，可以看到在香港島不同角落賽車的片段，逼真還原了香港島的街頭景觀。TDUSC 以一個極具影響力的神祕組織做背景，他們四處邀請會員參加賽車，為追求崇高的聲望和對賽車的熱愛而不斷競賽。玩家可以在遊戲中自由探索香港島，參與當地的競賽並使用自己改裝的賽車稱霸「Solar Crown」賽事。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1239524 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/unwire-1717144566-536x580.jpg" alt="TDUSC" width="536" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/unwire-1717144566-536x580.jpg 536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/unwire-1717144566.jpg 831w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 536px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/1249970/Test_Drive_Unlimited_Solar_Crown/">Steam</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">Test Drive Unlimited Solar Crown 將會於 9 月 12 日登陸 PC、PS5 與 Xbox Series X/S 平台。目前 Steam 上預購價為 $308，「Silver Sharps」和「Silver Streets」兩個 DLC 同捆包則為 $469，亦有推出 $556 的豪華版，除了包含上述 DLC 的內容之外更可以提早 7 天遊玩遊戲。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">資料來源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8GUCrMPJgkE">PlayStation</a>、<a href="https://gnn.gamer.com.tw/detail.php?sn=264451">巴哈姆特</a></p><p>圖片來源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8GUCrMPJgkE">PlayStation</a></p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/03/27/%e3%80%90%e8%a9%95%e6%b8%ac%e3%80%91ps5%e3%80%8a%e6%b5%aa%e4%ba%ba%e5%b4%9b%e8%b5%b7%e3%80%8b%e3%80%80%e5%b9%95%e6%9c%ab%e4%ba%82%e4%b8%96%e6%b4%bb%e5%87%ba%e8%87%aa%e7%94%b1/game-channel/game-review/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【評測】PS5《浪人崛起》　幕末亂世活出自由</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/31/gow5-on-pc/game-channel/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">《戰神：諸神黃昏》9 月登陸 PC　需要用 PSN 帳號登入才可玩</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/31/monsterhunterwilds/game-channel/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Monster Hunter Wilds 首段預告片【有片睇】新魔物 + 新坐騎 + 新玩法</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/31/tdusc-hk/game-channel/">賽車遊戲《Test Drive Unlimited》相隔 12 年推新作回歸，以香港島做主題、超逼真還原街景</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2024/05/31/tdusc-hk/game-channel/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
